songs.title: Dent freestyle
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: XXXTentacion]

Who who who! Young turn that shit up
*Laugh*

[Verse 1: XXXTentacion]

I’m not surprised that you’re tryna make a dent
Before you crash to the ground
And your just tryna do your best but vro, 877 cash now
*Laugh*

Cake in my mouth cuz a nigga hungerz, for plums, and others dumb thungs
But you thunk, you drunk, you smoked, you tryna make a dent, but nigga you a joke! (Ayy Nigga!)
